Loess Hills Prairie Seed Harvest

Hitchcock Nature Center

27792 Ski Hill Loop

Honey Creek, Iowa 51542

Map to Event

Tuesday, August 13, 2024

6:30pm · 8:00pm

Join our friends at Golden Hills RC&D and help collect native prairie seed! Volunteers will visit local prairie remnants and learn how to identify which plants are available for seed collection. The hand-collected seed will then be used for local prairie restoration and reconstruction projects. This event includes walking over steep, rugged terrain, so dress appropriately.

Read More

For the full event description, and more information, please visit the Pottawattamie Conservation website.
